# Transpiler corpus pin.
#
# Every file under tests/transpiler-corpus/<case>/{input.docs.json,
# expected.md} is hashed (SHA-256) and listed below in lexicographic
# order. These byte-identical fixtures are the golden test surface for
# the Rust transpiler.
#
# Update protocol when changing a fixture:
#   1. Edit the fixture intentionally (commit the change).
#   2. Run `cargo test -p melon-pan-core --test corpus_manifest` and
#      copy the assertion failure's "expected" line into this file.
#   3. Re-emit on the macOS / Windows ports and confirm they hash the
#      same bytes; commit the manifest update with all three.
#
# Format: `<hex digest>  <relative path under tests/transpiler-corpus/>`
# Lines starting with `#` are comments.
